json.text: This is Ember. Destructive and deadly.
Sacrificing safety for reckless abandon, she erupts into battle.
Ember’s abilities offset her fragility with pure offensive capability.
Fireball launches a fiery projectile towards your target, dealing high damage upon impact
and moderate damage to any nearby who stumble onto the lingering flames.
Accelerant blasts outward from Ember, stunning nearby enemies.
while also making them more susceptible to fire damage.
Fire Blast slams down a persistent ring of fire,
dealing high initial damage to enemies within its radius when cast
Some just want to watch the world burn, Tenno.
World on Fire follows Ember, causing fiery explosions while dealing high damage over time
to a limited number of targets.
Ember by nature is incredibly effective with flames,
but the use of mods will help her become even more deadly.
Adding strength mods will increase the damage output by all her abilities.
Adding duration mods will benefit Accelerant and Fire Blast.
Coupled with a ranged mod, World on Fire becomes even more effective.
Ember’s presence on the battlefield is devastating. Mind the heat, Tenno.
